        public static final java.lang.String POS_MODEL_FILE_PARAM
        "PosModelFile" is a required, single, string parameter that contains the file name of the part of speech tagger model. The model file name should end with ".bin.gz" or ".txt". If this is not the case, then please see resources/models/README.
